data.description: Incredible opportunity to own a  newly renovated single family home located just off the Green in vibrant downtown Bloomfield. Perfect combination of in-town living with lovely outdoor space to make your own. Only .4 miles to the Bloomfield train station and close to all of the local shops, restaurants, and parks. The first floor features a generous and brightly lit living room, spacious new kitchen with all new appliances which opens to a huge dining area with closet, and full bath. The second floor has a wonderful primary suite and huge second bedroom.  Don't miss the third floor bedroom with two large closets. This home was completely updated down to the studs and includes all new electrical, plumbing, windows, and flooring. Basement could be finished and is plumbed for a bath. All you need to do is unpack and enjoy all the area has to offer!
